main event: A UFO sighting was reported on 9 February 1955 in May Port, Florida, where an unidentified object emitted exhaust without leaving contrails.
interesting points: The exhaust from the object was observed to be 180 degrees in area and sharply defined,The observation lasted for two minutes,The sighting happened at an altitude where other known craft left no contrails,The report raises the possibility of the object being a known craft,The document is a record from Project Blue Book.
